            {
                "type": "stat_block_section",
                "subtype": "special_ability",
                "text": "As a standard action, the hierarch can psychically project terrifying visions that affect any number of creatures within 60 feet. Each affected creature attempts a Will save (DC = 8 + the hierarch\u2019s CR). If they fail, they\u2019re staggered for 1 round and shaken for 1d4 rounds. If they succeed, they\u2019re shaken for 1 round. After being affected by this ability, a creature is immune to that hierarch\u2019s zhufera visions for 1 hour. This is a mind-affecting ability.",
